message.content:
To help you develop a new investment strategy, I need to understand your financial situation and goals better. Here are a couple of questions to get us started:

1. What are your primary financial goals? (e.g., retirement, buying a home, education, wealth accumulation)
2. What is your risk tolerance? (e.g., conservative, moderate, aggressive)

Your answers will help me tailor a strategy that suits your needs!
